overview: El Phantasmo was founded in 2007 to provide high quality and affordable programming services to the IT and game developments industries. Our reputation is based strongly on our work in the mobile and entertainment sectors. Our portfolio spreads through mobile content like innovative apps, games, adverts and client services but also in webdevelopment, social network solutions or even highly specialized light controlling software.
